{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got in touch with him, and he helped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got some-- some lawyers in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you don't have to pay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we succeed to win your case, then they'll take 6% of the money I'll get from Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it worked out that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the way they were trying took me 13 years to get a cent out of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hornigbaum succeeded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after that, you know, I still were not working there, only a different place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And 1983-- before that, I was called three times to the Sydney German consulate to give, oh, not statements, but they will ask, do I know that German SS men, and do I not, from from Sobibor?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew them by name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then one day I was giving evidence, they brought in a very big photo-- photo album, and a lot of Germans and soldiers, SS men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to find somebody will the name of Gomerski.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a drunkard all the time and came with the [INAUDIBLE]-- in where the-- oh, the-- the crematoriums were and the-- and the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to find him, you know, in a photo to see if I recognized him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked over once.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I looked over-- I don't know how many times I looked over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said Gomerski's not in that album.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later on, they had, you know, for lunch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the secretary, who was sitting there and typing every word I was saying, she gave me the book.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said, look it over quiet now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're not here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You might find him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the photos were numbered, and the names were somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
